title: language example
pid: bee0b66f-a890-46f1-90be-712d79c468a5
body: |2-
  As a root or child of any node,
  the user should be able to insert a 'remote insertion' node.
  Each &-separated item in it is a title,
  or if it includes "/" characters, a contentward path to a terminus
  (so "a / b / c" represents a terminus c,
  such that there exist nodes matching the search terms a, b and c
  where a contains b and b contains c.
contains:
- c2a54a23-9b19-495c-8321-f9f41a4c24e9
